-- Air India on `Firm Path' to Recovery, Aviation Minister Praful Patel Says
-- Vipin V. Nair
-- 2010-07-25T11:45:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-25/air-india-on-firm-path-to-recovery-aviation-minister-praful-patel-says.html

          
          
             Air India, the national carrier, is
on a “firm path” toward recovery, Civil Aviation Minister
Praful Patel told reporters in Mumbai today.  
